languages.text: "У губернатора Вьятт все под контролем, Ваша Светлость. Народ еще волнуется, но после вашего вмешательства большинство мятежников и недовольных стихли".

traits.locale_text: "У губернатора Вьятт все под контролем, Ваше Благородие. Народ еще волнуется, но после вашего вмешательства большинтсво мятежников и недовольных стихли".

languages.text: "Governor Vyatt has everything well in hand, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The people are still unsettled, but after your intervention, most of the rebels and malcontents have quietened down."

languages.text: “一切都在维亚特总督的控制之中，大人。尽管人民并没有完全平静下来，但在您的干预之下，绝大部分叛乱分子与心怀不满的民众都安静下来了。”
languages.original_text: "Governor Vyatt has everything well in hand, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The people are still unsettled, but after your intervention, most of the rebels and malcontents have quietened down."

languages.text: «La gobernadora Vyatt lo tiene todo controlado, mi{mf|lord|lady}. La gente sigue inquieta, pero, tras su intervención, la mayor parte de los rebeldes y descontentos han dejado de dar problemas».
languages.original_text: "Governor Vyatt has everything well in hand, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The people are still unsettled, but after your intervention, most of the rebels and malcontents have quietened down."

languages.text: 「ビャット総督が全てを掌握しております、陛下。住民はまだ不安を抱いていますが、陛下が本件に介入してからは、反乱軍と不満分子の多くが落ち着きつつあります」
languages.original_text: "Governor Vyatt has everything well in hand, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The people are still unsettled, but after your intervention, most of the rebels and malcontents have quietened down."

languages.text: "Gouverneurin Vyatt hat alles unter Kontrolle, Eure {mf|Lordschaft|Ladyschaft}. Das Volk ist immer noch unruhig, aber nach Eurem Eingreifen sind die meisten Rebellen und Querulanten verstummt."
languages.original_text: "Governor Vyatt has everything well in hand, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The people are still unsettled, but after your intervention, most of the rebels and malcontents have quietened down."

languages.text: « La gouverneure Vyatt a la situation bien en main, Votre Seigneurie. Les habitants sont toujours perturbés, mais après votre intervention, la plupart des rebelles et des mécontents se sont calmés. »
languages.original_text: "Governor Vyatt has everything well in hand, Your {mf|Lordship|Ladyship}. The people are still unsettled, but after your intervention, most of the rebels and malcontents have quietened down."

languages.text: "Vali Vyatt her şeyi kontrol altında tutuyor {mf|Lord|Leydi} Hazretleri. Halk hâlâ huzursuz olsa da müdahalenizden sonra çoğu isyancı ve şikâyetçinin sesi kesildi."
